            "text": "The messengers? One Korea Network and the Korea Conservative Political Action Conference, wealthy pressure groups working to gin up tensions here and abroad. And as we highlight below in this edition of Weekend Reader, one Honolulu resident is the chief operative pulling the strings behind the scenes — and she may have a personal stake in the matter.",
